## Phase 2: Resizable Splitter System

### Goal
Replace fixed 40%/60% folder/notes split with user-adjustable, persisted splitter.

### Files to Create
- `src/hooks/useResizableSplitter.ts` - Reusable splitter logic

### Implementation
```tsx
// ResizableSplitter component
<div
  className="h-2 cursor-row-resize group relative"
  role="separator"
  aria-orientation="horizontal"
  aria-valuenow={position}
>
  {/* 8px hit area (4px visible + 4px each side) */}
  <div className="absolute inset-x-0 top-1/2 h-0.5 -translate-y-1/2
                  bg-border-light dark:bg-border-dark
                  group-hover:bg-accent-blue/50
                  transition-colors duration-fast" />
  {/* Grip dots on hover */}
  <div className="opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 flex gap-0.5 ...">
    <div className="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-text-tertiary" />
    <div className="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-text-tertiary" />
    <div className="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-text-tertiary" />
  </div>
</div>
```

### Features
- 8px drag area (current is 1px - unusable)
- Visual feedback on hover/drag
- Keyboard accessible (arrow keys)
- Double-click to reset to default
- Position persisted to localStorage

