## Phase 5: Responsive Design

### Breakpoints
| Breakpoint | Width | Behavior |
|------------|-------|----------|
| Mobile | <640px | Full-screen overlay sidebar, single pane |
| Tablet | 640-1024px | Collapsible sidebar (200-300px) |
| Desktop | 1024px+ | Full split view (200-500px sidebar) |

### Mobile Implementation
- Sidebar as drawer overlay (slide from left)
- Swipe from left edge to open
- Tap outside or swipe left to close
- Notes list becomes full-width
- Tap note → full-screen editor with back button

### View Mode System
```typescript
type NotesViewMode = 'split' | 'editor-only' | 'list-only';

// Keyboard shortcuts:
// Cmd+\ - Toggle sidebar (split <-> editor-only)
