## Phase 6: Animation & Polish

### Animation Standards
- `duration-fast`: 100ms (micro-interactions)
- `duration-standard`: 200ms (most UI)
- `duration-slow`: 300ms (sidebars, modals)
- GPU-accelerated: Only animate `transform` and `opacity`

### Specific Animations
| Interaction | Animation |
|-------------|-----------|
| Folder expand/collapse | height + opacity, 150ms |
| Sidebar width resize | transform (during drag), 200ms (settle) |
| Note hover | scale-[1.005], 100ms |
| Note selection | background-color, 150ms |
| Mobile sidebar | transform + opacity, 200ms spring |

### Accessibility
- `prefers-reduced-motion` support
- ARIA: `role="tree"`, `role="treeitem"`, `aria-expanded`, `aria-selected`
- Focus rings: `ring-2 ring-accent-blue ring-offset-2`
- Touch targets: minimum 44x44px
- Screen reader announcements for selection changes

